Class Summary
HVclient  
HVCommand HVComand - implements methods to form a queue of messages between sender and HVclient to communicate with Hvframe.
HVframe class HVframe - implements initialization of HVmainframe, starts 'client' to communicate with HVmainframe, starts 'monitor' to periodicaly looking of changing global summary numbers, asking new values for changing data (measurement voltage(MV),demand voltage(DV), measurement current(MC),channels status(ST) and others) from mainframe.
